After a long and grueling sword battle, both brothers were injured bad. The=
y both layed on the ground for a few seconds.

"Brother, it has to end this=
 way!" Sinister said.

"I shall triumph, as usual. Like when I killed out p=
arents." Sinesis said.

Sinister realized that his brother did lie to him a=
fter all, breaking their vow. Sinister played his whistle to Sinesis, telli=
ng him that he was the hunter once more. Sinesis tried to activate his jets=
, they wouldn't work. He remembered the first time he used those jets for a=
 good purpose, he used them to fly Quickstrike back to base. He came to the=
 planet searching for Hell Beast, but joined Megatron instead. Rattrap, Qui=
ckstrike, and Shredder were with Megatron. Sinesis almost got into a fight =
with Shredder as well. Sinister raised his sword, saying that evil shall be=
 vanquished in Cybertronian dialogue. Sinister plunged the sword into Sines=
is. Sinesis raised his sword into place and stabbed Sinister as well. Both =
fell flat and bled all over the battlefield...
